Lithuanian Athletics Championships (lt.  Lietuvos lengvosios atletikos empionatas)  national champsionhips in athletics, organizating by Athletic Federation of Lithuania. Recent competitions were held in S. Darius and S. Girnas Stadium in Kaunas since 2000. First competition was held in 1921. Women first time participated at 1922 championship. In past there was 20km and 20000 m walking, 2000 m steeplechase, 60 metres, decathlon and heptathlon events. Records set since 1921 
I read the paragraph on http://wikipedia.org
